    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically robust 2008 Porsche 911 Carrera (997.1), a purist\u2019s specification featuring the 3.6L M97 horizontally-opposed six-cylinder engine. This power plant delivers a linear torque curve and is mated to a precise 6-speed manual transaxle, ensuring total driver engagement. The chassis is equipped with Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM), providing adaptive damping that remains taut and responsive. Braking is handled by four-piston monobloc fixed calipers over vented rotors, showing no signs of fade under load. The vehicle exhibits excellent turn-in characteristics thanks to its rear-engine weight bias and well-maintained multi-link rear suspension geometry. Recent preventative maintenance ensures the IMS and RMS remain within operating tolerances. This is a high-performance driver\u2019s car optimized for the apex.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
